Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.38,0:00:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that you, Sis?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.00,0:00:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.86,0:00:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Feel free to leap into my arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.43,0:00:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.26,0:00:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though we've been apart for so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.40,0:00:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You're no fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.03,0:00:59.03,Default,chapter,0,0,0,,{OP}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.90,0:01:05.37,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,250)}Bored, sitting on the windowsill,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.37,0:01:13.50,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,250)}I frown at the wind to hide my awkwardness
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.71,0:01:21.59,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(280,0)\blur3.6\t(0,989,2,\blur0.6)}Hyouka
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.59,0:01:26.68,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,250)}I nod uncertainly as I shape
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.02,0:01:32.40,OP,,0,0,0,,the future in my hands feeling mighty
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.40,0:01:37.56,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,250)}I feel that the wind is bringing change
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.91,0:01:42.66,OP,,0,0,0,,I guess that's your fault for calling out to my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.41,0:01:49.74,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,250)}The cloudy sky tells a tale of what's to come
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.74,0:01:58.26,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,0)}Spread our wings with more courage than ever before
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.26,0:02:02.84,OP,,0,0,0,,Light and dark are still vague in the distance
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.84,0:02:09.10,OP,,0,0,0,,but still we want to know the reason behind kindness
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.10,0:02:13.68,OP,,0,0,0,,No one so far has ever reached
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.68,0:02:16.53,OP,,0,0,0,,the shining distance far beyond
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.53,0:02:25.15,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,350)}Let's get there before the past takes it all
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.00,0:02:29.00,Default,chapter,0,0,0,,{Part A}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.92,0:02:36.55,ep title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(859,476)\blur3.6\bord1.5\clip(129,831,155,899)\t(109,800,\clip(129,831,1170,899))\t(4154,4700,\clip(870,831,870,899))\pos(397.5,837)}To Be Needed
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.46,0:02:36.96,Default,,0,0,38,,You brought this from South America?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.72,0:02:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! You wanted something, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.46,0:02:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.44,0:02:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Good morning. Up next is today's forecast.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.31,0:03:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,How rare to see you watching TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.82,0:03:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with the paper?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.82,0:03:04.70,signs,,0,0,0,,{\fnCenturyOldStyle-Light\fax0.15\blur0.72\b1\c&H524B3D&\pos(1303.5,154.5)\fscx53\fscy57\frx0\fry350\frz7.146\1a&H0A&}Water
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.68,0:03:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}A Pacific anticyclone ensures clear \Nweather over most of western Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.68,0:03:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't feel like thinking right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.55,0:03:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You look like you've got time to spare.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.64,0:03:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Some areas may experience severely high\N temperatures climbing over 33 degrees Celsius.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.64,0:03:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,My schedule's packed today, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.34,0:03:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? What with?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.51,0:03:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Napping.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.65,0:03:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Please take precautions against heat exhaustion.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.69,0:03:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I know a part-time job that pays\N you 5,000 yen just for sitting there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.98,0:03:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}And now, the rain forecast.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.13,0:03:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.62,0:03:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}While it will be clear during the day, humid Pacific air masses may bring light showers in the evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.57,0:03:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You in or you out?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.04,0:03:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it's settled. I'll tell them you're in.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.40,0:03:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Tomorrow morning will bring cool temperatures typical of fall,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.14,0:03:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.86,0:03:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}but it will heat up considerably during the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.53,0:03:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget to put some on while you're working.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.86,0:03:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, this is Oreki.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.71,0:03:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Satoshi? It's been so long!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.86,0:03:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I arrived just a little while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.44,0:03:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Houtarou? Sure. Just a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.60,0:04:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Houtarou, Satoshi's on the phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.92,0:04:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Houtarou, have you finished that book you borrowed from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.95,0:04:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,If so, can I have it back?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.50,0:04:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I pick it up today?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.14,0:04:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Once I'm back from work.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.00,0:04:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.45,0:04:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Once I'm back from work.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.89,0:04:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You? {\i1}Working?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.78,0:04:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Did the heat fry your brain?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.51,0:04:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I just went with the flow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.10,0:04:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm filling in for some friend of \Nmy sis as a lifeguard at the pool.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.72,0:04:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, your sister. That explains it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.89,0:04:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Seeing you breaking a sweat \Nwould certainly be something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.69,0:04:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to get going, so I'll catch you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.85,0:04:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. I'll stop by later to see the legend at work.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.51,0:04:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever. Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.87,0:04:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Later.
