Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.40,0:05:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Houtarou!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.48,0:05:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. We're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.99,0:05:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't expecting all three of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.94,0:05:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I told them they could catch a glimpse of the rarest sight in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.20,0:05:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuku, you meant this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.29,0:05:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup! Houtarou working!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.94,0:05:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, it's quite a letdown.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.27,0:05:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.43,0:05:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that we're here, let's enjoy ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.88,0:05:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.45,0:05:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that we're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.90,0:05:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.42,0:05:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You makin' eyes at my woman?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.06,0:05:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.80,0:06:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.28,0:06:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, please calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.36,0:06:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.12,0:06:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}May I never have to deal with troublemakers. Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.02,0:06:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'm throwing it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.24,0:06:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.05,0:06:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.22,0:06:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.42,0:06:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Chitanda! Give it a good smack!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.52,0:06:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You're hopeless, Chi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.96,0:06:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Penalty dare for Chitanda!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.13,0:07:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry! I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.75,0:07:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We're ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.73,0:07:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.15,0:07:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.84,0:07:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.70,0:07:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Sliding time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.48,0:07:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.34,0:07:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Shift's up. You can take a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.96,0:07:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Oreki.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.96,0:07:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Mind if we join you for lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.04,0:07:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I would've made something nice if you \Nhadn't dragged us out at a moment's notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.61,0:07:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Address your complaints to Houtarou.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.22,0:07:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.36,0:08:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on. He's like a walking pile of laziness.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.68,0:08:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Then all of a sudden, he decides to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.76,0:08:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We couldn't miss this for the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.63,0:08:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Houtarou?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.08,0:08:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's lots of fun getting everyone together like this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.50,0:08:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.23,0:08:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Too bad he still sticks out like a sore thumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.66,0:08:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.56,0:08:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Houtarou. At a pool.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.22,0:08:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't argue with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.46,0:08:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You two are being mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.38,0:08:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Or Oreki in swimming gear.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.94,0:08:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.01,0:08:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Or just Houtarou in the sun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.54,0:08:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oreki in the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.86,0:08:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Houtarou and summer!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.50,0:08:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.42,0:08:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Oreki?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.13,0:08:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's head back to the pool.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.24,0:08:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. I'll clean up the trash.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.55,0:08:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll return the chairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.46,0:09:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.40,0:09:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on. Don't cry, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.81,0:09:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go buy another one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.55,0:09:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That startled me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.57,0:09:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.53,0:09:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you like your job?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.59,0:09:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.54,0:09:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to try it too, one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.32,0:09:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,They're so fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.11,0:09:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think they're planning to become professional swimmers?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.42,0:09:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Some of them might end up winning gold medals.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.49,0:10:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Dunno about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.72,0:10:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,If they're born to win one, they will.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.31,0:10:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Special people can do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.57,0:10:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Ordinary people can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.81,0:10:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to be special, Oreki?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.42,0:10:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.60,0:10:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Come what may, I'm just an ordinary guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.58,0:10:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You {\i1}are{\i0} special, Oreki!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.55,0:10:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You're special to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.02,0:10:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Fukube and Mayaka are too!{T.T}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.57,0:10:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone who's close to me is special!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.16,0:10:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,From your point of view, yeah, but I meant on a more gener—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.83,0:10:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.86,0:10:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to worry about being special or ordinary compared to other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.51,0:10:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,If there's just one person out there \Nwho considers me special, I'm happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.56,0:11:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, I mean—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.72,0:11:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
