Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.98,0:11:11.98,Default,chapter,0,0,0,,{Part B}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.38,0:11:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.91,0:11:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You {\i1}are{\i0} special, Oreki!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.54,0:11:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.85,0:11:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oreki, shift's up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.25,0:11:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Go take a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.78,0:11:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... Oreki.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.60,0:12:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something I just can't stop thinking about.{KININARIMASU}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.20,0:12:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, it's basically part of your job.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.56,0:12:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you see that lady in the red swimsuit?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.00,0:12:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,When we finished lunch, I saw \Nsomething white on her left ear.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.36,0:12:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's not there now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.06,0:12:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you even notice something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.58,0:12:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it was just by chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.71,0:12:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So? What does that have to do with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.08,0:12:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Quite a lot, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.84,0:12:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What if it was a stud or an earring?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.17,0:12:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,If someone stepped on it, they might get hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.41,0:12:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oreki, could you help us search for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.74,0:12:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Across the entire pool grounds?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.90,0:12:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.21,0:13:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure she had something on her ear?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.73,0:13:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.68,0:13:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why don't you ask {\i1}her{\i0} before you go looking?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.02,0:13:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to do that, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.94,0:13:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,she isn't exactly easy to approach.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.10,0:13:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like you're asking her something dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.64,0:13:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.93,0:13:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Then {\i1}you{\i0} go and ask her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.07,0:13:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.25,0:13:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, Oreki!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.28,0:13:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the lifeguard here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.64,0:13:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Houtarou?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.82,0:13:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stop thinking about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.83,0:13:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? The girl with that guy who flipped out?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.04,0:13:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, this is gonna be a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.53,0:13:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I really don't want any trouble, so could you just look for it or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.24,0:13:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but I can't do it alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.12,0:14:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll tell the other lifeguards to check the poolside.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.72,0:14:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you look in the pool?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.37,0:14:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.70,0:14:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll help too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.24,0:14:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.48,0:14:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess I gotta, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.46,0:14:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.74,0:14:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But... however should we look for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.90,0:14:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have a better chance if we split up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.40,0:14:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.66,0:14:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think, Oreki?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.74,0:14:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.89,0:14:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, show some spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.88,0:14:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed! It's time to earn your lifeguard's wage!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.36,0:14:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,At least decide how we should split up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.32,0:14:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, fine. I'll take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.98,0:14:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, the area around the stairs is yours, Chitanda and Mayaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.12,0:14:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Houtarou gets the slide,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.26,0:14:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'll handle the diving board.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.42,0:14:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.02,0:14:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.07,0:14:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.20,0:14:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.41,0:14:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Houtarou,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.33,0:15:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,is this job something you have to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.48,0:15:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Dunno.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.68,0:15:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.18,0:15:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the point of your motto, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.19,0:15:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.69,0:15:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I wanted to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.99,0:15:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care if you're griping, but at least react {\i1}somehow{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.27,0:15:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, it's no fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.57,0:15:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,See you around.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.01,0:16:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oreki!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.42,0:16:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No slacking off.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.55,0:16:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not slacking off.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.16,0:16:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I just got out to dispose of a piece of glass.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.14,0:16:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.30,0:16:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously, Oreki, just looking at you tires me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.20,0:16:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a real pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.12,0:16:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Feel free not to look, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.72,0:16:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,In the past, you could piss me off just by being there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.76,0:16:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a pain too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.49,0:16:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a pain either way, but if I had to pick,{dattara semete}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.48,0:16:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd rather you went back to your old self.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.62,0:17:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Even that was better than this \Nunresponsive lump you are now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.94,0:17:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Better, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.64,0:17:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you find it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.82,0:17:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,No, but I'm thinking we might not have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.18,0:17:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So you figured something out, Houtarou?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.68,0:17:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.06,0:17:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Chitanda, are you sure it was an earring?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.63,0:17:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.42,0:18:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm sure she had something white on her left ear.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.70,0:18:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If she was only wearing one, it's more likely it was a stud.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.40,0:18:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not it. I'm not asking \Nwhat kind of accessory it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.01,0:18:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,More like, are you sure it was even an accessory at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.12,0:18:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.78,0:18:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.55,0:18:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If she had pierced ears, she wouldn't be pounding them like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.76,0:18:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.47,0:18:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So she probably had something\N stuck on her ear without knowing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.50,0:18:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But what could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.59,0:18:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.26,0:18:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Satoshi, could you pick up Ibara?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.44,0:18:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.52,0:18:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.35,0:18:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Then how about Chitanda?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.32,0:18:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Having Chi pick me up isn't any better!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.56,0:18:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like I'm a little kid! It's embarrassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.08,0:18:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's the idea. I want to see how a kid would do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.34,0:19:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do we even need to do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.30,0:19:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,To test my theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.04,0:19:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Your theory? For this case?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.89,0:19:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.24,0:19:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.10,0:19:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine. I give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.12,0:19:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You're quite strong, Chitanda.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.64,0:19:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that supposed to mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.85,0:19:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing! I just meant... it takes a lot of strength to pick up people, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.40,0:19:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.56,0:19:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You knew what?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.76,0:19:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Her hands. They naturally rest on the shoulders.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.76,0:19:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I get down now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.24,0:19:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.78,0:19:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.14,0:19:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.80,0:20:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Earlier, that woman had that kid in her arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.35,0:20:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I assume they're mother and son or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.06,0:20:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What if she picked him up while \Nhe had an ice cream in his hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.74,0:20:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.96,0:20:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The ice cream would be right next to her ear!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.42,0:20:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.76,0:20:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So if it's not there now...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.42,0:20:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It might have washed off in the water, \Nor someone might have told her about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.75,0:20:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.84,0:20:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... Oreki...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.32,0:20:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.41,0:20:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.23,0:20:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I think the way you solve these cases is really amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.37,0:20:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Your praise falls on barren ground with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.50,0:20:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.95,0:21:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I've missed that cynicism of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.72,0:21:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.01,0:21:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup. When you're not like that, it throws us all off.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.28,0:21:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh right. I haven't thanked you yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.05,0:21:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much, Oreki!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.42,0:21:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the trouble I caused you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.44,0:21:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.91,0:21:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Chi...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.56,0:21:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I was the one who thought it was \Nan earring or a stud or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.64,0:21:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Oreki.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.53,0:21:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever. Just stop apologizing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.22,0:21:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! All that searching made me hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.92,0:21:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should grab some ice cream t—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.26,0:21:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Why'd you freeze after saying ice cre—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.37,0:21:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hyouka{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.97,0:21:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuku, you promised you'd have your manuscript for {\i1}Hyouka{\i0} done today!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.20,0:21:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Well? Is it ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.24,0:21:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I guess you could say that... More or less...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.27,0:21:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're {\i1}not{\i0} finished, are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.52,0:22:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I guess you could say that too...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.47,0:22:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no "too" about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.73,0:22:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuku, you're coming with me right now, and you're finishing that manuscript!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.62,0:22:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not letting you out of my sight until it's done!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.35,0:22:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's just a little more! I can do it myself, honest!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.68,0:22:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Not on your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.32,0:22:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Chi, Oreki, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.02,0:22:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We're gonna head off now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.06,0:22:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,See you tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.25,0:22:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Farewe—
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.68,0:22:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope they get that manuscript done.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.06,0:22:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.61,0:22:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, they say one should be glad to be needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.56,0:22:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,They should just do their best.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.87,0:22:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,To be needed...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.96,0:22:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I needed your help today once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.72,0:22:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for all the trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.43,0:22:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You should be. It's a real pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.52,0:22:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That's mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.64,0:22:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But I guess I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.56,0:22:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.14,0:23:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, Oreki, how did you know the white thing was ice cream?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.74,0:23:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, that?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.18,0:23:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Look around. It's the only white thing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.02,0:23:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, except for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.85,0:23:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose I'll take my leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.36,0:23:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck with the rest of your work.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.80,0:23:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.80,0:23:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.23,0:23:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Your turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.38,0:23:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.43,0:23:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What a drag.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.96,0:24:02.96,Default,chapter,0,0,0,,{ED}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.92,0:24:10.68,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)\blur2.4}Let us meet in a blissful dream tonight, let it be our love
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.68,0:24:14.68,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)\blur2.4}Find me, I beg you
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.68,0:24:19.77,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,350)\blur2.4}We promised to meet, drifting in and out of sleep
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.16,0:24:40.92,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)\blur2.4}This sprouting warmth confuses us
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.00,0:24:51.85,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,150)\blur2.4}Don't you understand this feeling yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.43,0:24:57.94,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,150)\blur2.4}Normally such random glances hold no meaning
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.94,0:25:03.27,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,450)\blur2.4}Isn't it the same when making friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.27,0:25:09.03,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,150)\blur2.4}The little shooting stars we wish upon, vanishing into the dawn
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.03,0:25:13.99,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,150)\blur2.4}are a magic that only unfolds in the night
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.99,0:25:20.79,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,150)\blur2.4}Let us meet in a blissful dream tonight, let it be our love
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.79,0:25:24.80,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,150)\blur2.4}Find me, I beg you
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.80,0:25:29.76,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,350)\blur2.4}We promised to meet, drifting in and out of sleep
